    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><p>This post is part of a <a href="http://befused.com/drupal/programmatically">series of posts</a> on making changes in Drupal programmatically rather than in the Drupal interface.</p>
<p>In this tutorial, we will be programmatically assigning role(s) to user(s). You would typically do this in a <a href="/drupal/site-deployment-module">site deployment module</a> in order to automate this task rather than having to manually assign the roles in the Drupal UI.</p>
